text:
Ensures medium- and long-term fiscal and debt sustainability;   
Begins addressing past fiscal policy pro-cyclicality; and protects the budget from the volatility of oil revenue to prevent disruptive changes in spending plans;   
Contributes to closing the large infrastructure gaps by allocating the bulk of oil revenue to investment spending;   
Takes into account expenditure absorptive capacity to avoid upward pressures on domestic prices and preserve the quality of public expenditures;   
Pursues a prudent borrowing policy; and   
Helps building resource buffers for future generations.
